{"tid":836040,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[10月新番播緊]JoJo的奇妙冒險 第5部黃金之風  ジョジョの奇妙な冒険Parte5 黄金の風 集中討論","createTime":"2018-09-25T11:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T20:32:31.000Z","uid":3020,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"153b5bd52c1fd7b242543ea6f6bf14f399331412","tid":836040,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T11:03:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/190142_a0786527689bac63d9c21a32a85c2701.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F190142_a0786527689bac63d9c21a32a85c2701.jpg&h=e2a91ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先行上映會播緊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R2600LHuK34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR2600LHuK34&d=Y0wifcN3F%2FuK9vkAND7tgsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=82c7f909\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R2600LHuK34</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n　住在義大利的拿坡里的青年 喬魯諾．喬巴拿，是有著喬斯達家的宿敵．DIO 血統的兒子。小時候備受欺凌的他，以救了一名流氓為契機，讓他是學到了「相信他人」。對於這位不忘恩情、並帶有敬意與他來往的這名流氓，深深地吸引了他的心。就這樣，讓喬魯諾是憧憬成為一名「流氓巨星」。15 歲那年，因和黑道組織「熱情」起了糾紛，也讓他是被人給盯上...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\npv<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R92KmKcg07Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR92KmKcg07Y&d=Y0wifcN3F%2FuK9vkAND7tgsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=099e3f52\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R92KmKcg07Y</a><br />\n<br />\n先行上映會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R2600LHuK34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR2600LHuK34&d=Y0wifcN3F%2FuK9vkAND7tgsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=82c7f909\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R2600LHuK34</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nstaff<br />\n原作：荒木飛呂彦（集英社ジャンプ コミックス刊）<br /